---
title: Smart Mexican Double Shrimp Skillet with Guacamole
description: Tonight's skillet dinner is packed with delights, from Mexican-style spices and fresh cilantro to creamy guacamole! A pepper and zucchini hash rounds it all out for a delicious yet light meal.

